      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节香瓜子葵花子促销页面</title>\n<style>\n:root {\n    --color-red: #D62828;\n    --color-orange: #F77F00;\n    --color-light: #F4F4F5;\n    --color-gold: #FFD700;\n    --color-primary: #D62828;\n}\n\nbody {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-family: \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    background-color: var(--color-light);\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\nheader, nav, section, footer, aside {\n    padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n.hero-section {\n    background-color: var(--color-red);\n    color: white;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 2rem 1rem;\n}\n\n.hero-section h1 {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.hero-section p {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n}\n\n.product-spec {\n    background-color: white;\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    margin: 1rem auto;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n}\n\n.price-box {\n    background-color: var(--color-gold);\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    margin: 1rem auto;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n}\n\n.price-box h2 {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.promotion-tags {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    margin: 1rem 0;\n}\n\n.promotion-tags span {\n    background-color: var(--color-orange);\n    color: white;\n    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n}\n\n.purchase-channel {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 2rem 0;\n}\n\n.purchase-channel button {\n    background-color: var(--color-primary);\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n    margin: 0 0.5rem;\n    font-size: 1rem;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.purchase-channel button:hover {\n    background-color: #b81f1f;\n}\n\n.cart-module {\n    background-color: white;\n    padding: 1rem;\n    margin: 1rem;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n}\n\n.category-nav ul {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n    margin: 0;\n}\n\n.category-nav li {\n    background-color: var(--color-orange);\n    color: white;\n    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.coupon-section {\n    background-color: white;\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    margin: 1rem auto;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n}\n\n.footer-info {\n    background-color: var(--color-red);\n    color: white;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n.footer-info nav {\n    margin-top: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.footer-info nav a {\n    color: white;\n    margin: 0 0.5rem;\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .hero-section h1 {\n        font-size: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    .price-box h2 {\n        font-size: 1.2rem;\n    }\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<section class=\"hero-section\" id=\"hero-section\">\n    <h1>春节香瓜子葵花子盛大促销</h1>\n    <p>浓浓年味，香脆可口，陪伴团圆时刻的最佳选择</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"product-spec\" id=\"product-spec\">\n    <h2>规格与卖点</h2>\n    <p>精选瓜子，500g/袋，产自优质葵花产区，颗粒饱满，香味扑鼻，精美包装，年味十足</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"price-box\" id=\"price-box\">\n    <h2>促销价：￥19.9</h2>\n    <p>原价￥29.9，限时立减￥10，机会不容错过</p>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"promotion-tags\" id=\"promotion-tags\">\n    <span>限时优惠 02:15:30</span>\n    <span>热销中 · 库存不足</span>\n</div>\n\n<section class=\"purchase-channel\" id=\"purchase-channel\">\n    <button>加入购物车</button>\n    <button>立即购买</button>\n</section>\n\n<aside class=\"cart-module\" id=\"cart-module\">\n    <h2>我的购物车</h2>\n    <p>已选商品列表及数量调整功能，结算更方便</p>\n</aside>\n\n<nav class=\"category-nav\" id=\"category-nav\">\n    <ul>\n        <li>坚果炒货</li>\n        <li>糖果零食</li>\n        <li>饮料酒水</li>\n        <li>腊味干货</li>\n        <li>礼盒礼品</li>\n    </ul>\n</nav>\n\n<section class=\"coupon-section\" id=\"coupon-section\">\n    <h2>优惠券领取</h2>\n    <p>满50减5元，满100减15元，点击立即领取并在下单时使用</p>\n</section>\n\n<footer class=\"footer-info\" id=\"footer-info\">\n    <p>© 2024 春节特惠 · 新春快乐</p>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#\">联系我们</a>\n        <a href=\"#\">售后服务</a>\n        <a href=\"#\">帮助中心</a>\n    </nav>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
